<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AgroPal - Smart Farming Companion</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/style.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
    
</head>
<body>
    
  <%- include("./includes/navbar.ejs") %>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <h1>Revolutionizing Agriculture with Smart Technology</h1>
                <p>AgroPal integrates IoT and Machine Learning to optimize irrigation, improve crop yields, and make farming sustainable.</p>
                <div class="hero-buttons">
                    <a href="/predict" class="btn primary">Get Started</a>
                    <a href="#features" class="btn secondary">Learn More</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-image">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1499529112087-3cb3b73cec95?q=80&w=1974&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D" alt="Smart Farming Illustration">
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="features" class="features">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Key Features</h2>
            <div class="features-grid">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-tint"></i>
                    <h3>Smart Irrigation</h3>
                    <p>Automated watering based on real-time soil moisture and weather data, reducing water waste by 30-50%.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
                    <h3>Crop Prediction</h3>
                    <p>ML algorithms analyze historical data to predict future crop yields and optimize planting strategies.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-bug"></i>
                    <h3>Disease Detection</h3>
                    <p>AI-powered image processing to detect diseases & pests early, providing timely warnings to farmers.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-bell"></i>
                    <h3>Activity Reminders</h3>
                    <p>Automated alerts for planting, fertilizing, and harvesting based on optimal timing.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-flask"></i>
                    <h3>Fertilizer Optimization</h3>
                    <p>Recommends the right type and amount of fertilizers for optimal growth and soil health.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i>
                    <h3>Mobile Access</h3>
                    <p>Monitor and control your farm from anywhere with our optional mobile application.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="technology" class="technology">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Our Technology Stack</h2>
            <div class="tech-stack">
                <div class="tech-item">
                    <img src="https://icon-library.com/images/sensor-icon-png/sensor-icon-png-11.jpg" alt="IoT">
                    <h3>IoT Sensors</h3>
                    <p>Real-time monitoring of soil moisture, temperature, and humidity.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="tech-item">
                    <img src="https://icon-library.com/images/machine-learning-icon/machine-learning-icon-28.jpg" alt="Machine Learning">
                    <h3>Machine Learning</h3>
                    <p>Predictive analytics for irrigation scheduling and yield prediction.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="tech-item">
                    <img src="/assets/cloud-storage.png" alt="Cloud">
                    <h3>Cloud Platform</h3>
                    <p>AWS/Google Cloud for secure data storage and processing.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="tech-item">
                    <img src="https://icon-library.com/images/phone_icon_png_white_1016064.png" alt="Mobile">
                    <h3>Mobile Interface</h3>
                    <p>Optional Flutter app for on-the-go farm management.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="benefits" class="benefits">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Benefits for Farmers</h2>
            <div class="benefits-content">
                <div class="benefits-text">
                    <ul>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Reduce water wastage by 20-30% through precise irrigation</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Increase crop productivity by 15-25% with optimal conditions</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Lower operational costs by reducing labor dependency</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Prevent over-irrigation and soil degradation</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Gain technological literacy with advanced farming tools</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Adaptable to diverse farm sizes and crop types</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="benefits-image">
                    <img src="https://t4.ftcdn.net/jpg/05/95/55/89/360_F_595558921_z1JnF4ieH75XlWoDPuh1Os97QkPnb4dx.jpg" alt="Happy Farmer">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact" class="contact">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            <div class="contact-content">
                <div class="contact-info">
                    <h3>Get in Touch</h3>
                    <p><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> en22cs301104@medicaps.ac.in</p>
                    <p><i class="fas fa-phone"></i> +91 831 984 2357</p>
                    <p><i class="fas fa-globe"></i> yourcompany.com</p>
                    <div class="social-links">
                        <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a>
                        <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
                        <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i></a>
                        <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="contact-form">
                    <form>
                        <input type="text" placeholder="Your Name" required>
                        <input type="email" placeholder="Your Email" required>
                        <input type="tel" placeholder="Phone Number">
                        <textarea placeholder="Your Message" required></textarea>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn primary">Send Message</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="footer-content">
                <div class="footer-logo">
                    <span>AgroPal</span>
                    <p>A Smart Farming Companion</p>
                </div>
                <div class="footer-links">
                    <h3>Quick Links</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li><a href="#features">Features</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#technology">Technology</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#benefits">Benefits</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="footer-newsletter">
                    <h3>Subscribe to Updates</h3>
                    <form>
                        <input type="email" placeholder="Your Email">
                        <button type="submit" class="btn secondary">Subscribe</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-bottom">
                <p>&copy; 2023 AgroPal. All Rights Reserved.</p>
                <p>PRESENTED BY: AMAN GOUR – EN22CS301104 | ANANT DOSI – EN22CS301116</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>